  "notes": "Cloud Accelerate Factory is a benefit within Azure Accelerate designed to help you jumpstart your Azure projects with zero-cost deployment support from Microsoft experts. This benefit is all about helping you move faster, maximize your investments, and scale your cloud journey with confidence.\n\nCloud Accelerate Factory provides value in three main ways: \nFirst, and maybe most important, Microsoft experts can assist in deploying over 30 Azure services at zero cost. \nSecond, it is built on insights, patterns, and best practices from thousands of customer deployments bringing proven, repeatable frameworks to projects. \nThird, it helps maximize investments by offloading repeatable and predictable technical tasks to Factory experts, teams can stay focused on high value, strategic work. \n \nWe say ”jumpstart” intentionally — because that’s exactly what the Factory enables. Whether it’s rehosting, refactoring, or migrating workloads, it gives you the hands-on support to scale your Azure projects further and faster.\n\nhttps://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/solutions/azure-accelerate#Cloud-Accelerate-Factory\n\n-------\n\nDetails about Factory offer: https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azuremigrationblog/introducing-cloud-accelerate-factory-unlock-zero-cost-deployment-assistance-for-/4409779\nDeployment assistance is offered at no additional cost to customers; however, eligibility is subject to meeting specific conditions including project scope, timing, and alignment with Factory-supported workloads. Availability may vary by region and engagement type.."
